C.A.S.  => clearing turns, altitude, safe area

1.  carb heat
2.  70 KTS, full flaps, descent 500 FPM 
3.  throttle off
4.  pitch up until stall > "imminant stall"
5.  let nose drop over, release backpressure 
6.  level pitch attitue & full throttle
7.  carb heat 


